  "text": "CNS-specific PPARGC1A transcripts are initiated in exon B1 followed by exons B4 and/or B5 and exon 2-exon 13 [CITATION_1] (Supplementary Material Fig. 1 ). RNA integrity scores showed no associations with age, sex, brain region, disease status or post-mortem time. Similarly, RPLP0 levels used for normalization of transcript levels revealed no associations with age, sex or post-mortem time.",
